data.title: Ella Wishes You A Swinging Christmas: Ruby Red Vinyl LP
data.meta_description: An iconic Christmas album, released for the first time on “Ruby Red” vinyl with a new collectable cover.The legendary Ella Fitzgerald sings (and swings) Jingle Bells; Sleigh Ride; Winter Wonderland; and more on this classic Christmas album!
